name: Cannot pay more than the Gift card Balance

steps.name: Given I am on the HOME page
When I clock in the timesheet with PIN "4040"
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('4', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('0', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('4', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'PASSWORD' }) }).getByText('0', { exact: true })
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title') }).locator('div.MuiDialogActions-root').getByRole('button', { name: 'CONFIRM', exact: true })
Then I should see the employee "Aubrey" in the employee list
Then I should see the "Ticket View" screen
And I should see the "Manicure" service
When I add the "Manicure" service to my cart
Then I should see my cart showing 1 item added
When I select the service "Manicure" in my cart
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('ul.xTicketFunctions__menu li').getByText('CHANGE PRICE', { exact: true }).first()
Click locator('ul.xTicketFunctions__menu li').getByText('CHANGE PRICE', { exact: true }).first()
When I click on the "Pay" button
And I select the "Gift" payment type
Then I should see the gift card balance "$20.00" visible
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('.xTicketFunsGiftCard__info > span').filter({ has: locator('span').filter({ hasText: 'BALANCE' }) }).first()
Expect "toContainText" locator('.xTicketFunsGiftCard__info > span').filter({ has: locator('span').filter({ hasText: 'BALANCE' }) }).first().locator('span').last()
When I wait for the page fully loaded
And I click on the "OK" button
And I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should see the payment Gift history "Gift (2020) $20.00" visible

Expect "toBeVisible" locator('ul.xTicketFunctions__payment--list li').filter({ has: locator('span.name').filter({ hasText: 'Gift (2020)' }) }).filter({ has: locator('span.amt').filter({ hasText: '$20.00' }) })

Expect "toContainText" locator('ul.xTicketFunctions__payment--list li').filter({ has: locator('span.name').filter({ hasText: 'Gift (2020)' }) }).filter({ has: locator('span.amt').filter({ hasText: '$20.00' }) }).locator('span.name')

Expect "toContainText" locator('ul.xTicketFunctions__payment--list li').filter({ has: locator('span.name').filter({ hasText: 'Gift (2020)' }) }).filter({ has: locator('span.amt').filter({ hasText: '$20.00' }) }).locator('span.amt')
When I select the "Gift" payment type
And I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should see the card value "$20.00" visible
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('.xTicketFunsGiftCard__info > span').filter({ has: locator('span').filter({ hasText: 'CARD VALUE' }) }).first()
Expect "toContainText" locator('.xTicketFunsGiftCard__info > span').filter({ has: locator('span').filter({ hasText: 'CARD VALUE' }) }).first().locator('span').last()
When I click on the "OK" button
Then I should see the toast message "Gift Card #2020 does not have enough funds to pay." visible
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('.MuiAlert-message').filter({ hasText: 'Gift Card #2020 does not have enough funds to pay.' })
When I click on the "Cancel" button
And I wait for the page fully loaded
And I select the "Cash" payment type
Then I should see a popup dialog with title "Close Ticket"
And I should see a popup dialog with content "CHANGE$0.00OK"
When I click on the "OK" button in the popup dialog
Then I should see the selected "SERVICE" tab on the Home page
When I select the "CLOSED TICKET" tab
And I wait for the page fully loaded
And I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should see the last ticket of payment "$35.70"
When I reopen ticket with payment amount "$35.70"
And I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should see the "Ticket View" screen
And I should see the user info "Aubrey" in the ticket
When I click on the "Void Ticket" button
Expect "toBeVisible" getByRole('button', { name: 'Void Ticket', exact: true })
Click getByRole('button', { name: 'Void Ticket', exact: true })
And I select the reason "System Test"
Then I should see a popup dialog with title "Confirm Void"
When I click on the "confirm" button in the popup dialog
Then I should see the selected "SERVICE" tab on the Home page
